graph.layout.router.orthogonal

Class OrthogonalEdgeRouter<V extends Vertex,E extends Edge<V>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • graph.layout.router.orthogonal.OrthogonalEdgeRouter<V,E>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - The vertex type
    E - The edge type

    public class OrthogonalEdgeRouter<V extends Vertex,E extends Edge<V>>
extends java.lang.Object
    Part of the orthogonal graph drawing algorithm. Routes edges so that the number of edge breaks is minimized and there is no edge overlapping. Work in progress.
    Author:
    Renata
